    "7 RAG allows information to be dynamically retrieved from medical databases during the model generation process, enriching the output with medical knowledge without the need to train the model.",
    "review were resolved through discussion with the author FB.",
    "In cases of studies with incomplete data, we have tried to contact the corresponding authors for clarification or additional information.",
